@startuml stm_primary
title <<stm>> CCamera Primary State Machine
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor<<browse>> #e3f2fd
    BorderColor<<browse>> #1565c0
    FontColor<<browse>> #0d47a1
    BackgroundColor<<terminal>> #e8f5e9
    BorderColor<<terminal>> #2e7d32
}
skinparam shadowing false
top to bottom direction

state "pre_construct" as Pre <<browse>>
state "active" as Active <<browse>>
state "destroyed" as Dead <<terminal>>

Pre -down-> Active : construct
Active --> Active : set_target/direction/distance/up_direction\nset_viewing_angle/aspect_ratio/clipping_planes\n(each fires GetChangeEvent)
Active --> Active : set_field_of_view(MaxSize)\n[fires change TWICE indirectly]
Active --> Active : recalc_xform / recalc_projection\n(mutable cache update; no fire)
Active -down-> Dead : destruct

note right of Active
    OBSERVABLE: 8 setters fire
    m_eventChange. SetFieldOfView
    is a convenience that calls
    SetClippingPlanes + SetDistance
    -- fires TWICE.
end note
@enduml
